race.comment: ONE STEP UP (2) was seventh in a Grade 5 two back then found trouble in the run and failed to finish at The Gardens last time. Should be in this for a long way. TARAWI BANJO (1) drew the inside and won last time at The Gardens and distance (29.74) after missing the jump, scoring by one length. Must include in calculations. ASHES TO ASHES (4) is having his first start around this track. In the money last start when third (22.54) at Bulli over 400m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Can feature again. FRANKLY (7) cannot be written off despite a miss here at her latest outing.
